title: Chef quest
data:
The [Chef](/wiki/Chef "Chef") [quest](/wiki/Quest "Quest") sees you fighting [The Immortal Rot](/index.php?title=The_Immortal_Rot\&action=edit\&redlink=1 "The Immortal Rot (page does not exist)") for [The Deluxe Yendorian Knife](/index.php?title=The_Deluxe_Yendorian_Knife\&action=edit\&redlink=1 "The Deluxe Yendorian Knife (page does not exist)"). It is a copy of the defunct [Doppelganger quest](/wiki/Doppelganger_quest "Doppelganger quest").

[ ]

## Levels

### Home

Here you meet your besieged class leader, the [Supreme Chef](/index.php?title=Supreme_Chef\&action=edit\&redlink=1 "Supreme Chef (page does not exist)"), next to a treasure chest and surrounded by 8 remaining [kitchen porters](/index.php?title=Kitchen_porter\&action=edit\&redlink=1 "Kitchen porter (page does not exist)"). You arrive from the portal in the top left, immediately beset by 8 [giant beetles](/wiki/Giant_beetle "Giant beetle") and 4 [bloodworms](/wiki/Bloodworm "Bloodworm"). There are 2 [polymorph traps](/wiki/Polymorph_trap "Polymorph trap") barring your entrance to the structure and 4 other random traps. This floor is lit, teleportation is blocked, and the walls and ground are undiggable.
